---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="About flpvvvv - Data Scientist">
  <header class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="font-sans text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">
      About Me
    </h1>
  </header>

  <div class="space-y-8">
    <section>
      <h2 class="font-sans text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">
        Hello!
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm flpvvvv, a data scientist passionate about understanding the world through data. I believe that statistics is the art of asking the right questions and finding meaningful answers in numbers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-sans text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">
        What I Do
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I explore the intersection of statistics, machine learning, and data analysis. My work involves turning complex datasets into actionable insights, building predictive models, and communicating findings in clear, compelling ways.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-sans text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">
        This Blog
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        This space serves as my digital notebook where I document my learning journey through statistics and data science. The posts here are largely based on my notes from the <strong>MITx: 18.6501x Fundamentals of Statistics</strong> course on edX, covering topics from probability theory to Bayesian statistics.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
        I believe in learning by teaching, and writing these notes helps me solidify my understanding while potentially helping others on similar journeys.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="font-sans text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-4">
        Connect
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Feel free to reach out via email or follow me on Twitter for occasional thoughts on data science and statistics.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="mailto:flpvvvv@live.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 rounded-lg text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"></path>
            <path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"></path>
          </svg>
          Email
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/flpvvvv" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 rounded-lg text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"></path>
          </svg>
          Twitter
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/flpvvvv" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-600 rounded-lg text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>